cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.LG

This paper involves the analysis of emotionally annotated comments in online datasets, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves statistical analysis, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of large datasets also suggests the possibility of cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
